{"title":"临淄古车马馆随想","authors":["宋道敏"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":5,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"临淄古车马馆随想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋道敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本应腾飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却被累累黄土掩没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以为满足了帝王的贪欲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实它们醒着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮还绕着逐鹿的硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马蹄还沾着血腥的征尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使被殉葬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁死也作驰骋形状"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉两千六百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许想让岁月凝固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但无数车轮仍颠簸前行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不肯就此化作了泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当岁月走上高速公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亦是古车马当年梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的对话十分深奥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风细雨作沉思状"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}